'''夏威夷僧海豹'''（學名：''Neomonachus schauinslandi''）是[[僧海豹屬|僧海豹屬]]下的一種[[瀕危物種|瀕危物種]]，原產於[[夏威夷群島|夏威夷群島]]，因而得名。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.monachus-guardian.org/factfiles/hawai01.htm |title=Hawaiian Monk Seal, Monachus schauinslandi |year=2006 |publisher=monachus-guardian.org |accessdate=2011-05-23 |archive-date=2013-08-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6JBcyKjN9?url=http://www.monachus-guardian.org/factfiles/hawai01.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>此外它也是[[夏威夷灰白蝙蝠|夏威夷灰白蝙蝠]]之外當地唯一的原生哺乳動物。<ref name=Nitta>{{cite journal |last=Nitta |first=Eugene |author2=Henderson JR |title=A review of interactions between Hawaii's fisheries and protected species |journal=Marine Fisheries Review |year=1993 |volume=55 |series=83 |issue=2 |url=http://spo.nmfs.noaa.gov/mfr552/mfr55210.pdf |format=pdf |accessdate=2011-05-23 |archive-date=2011-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827192045/http://spo.nmfs.noaa.gov/mfr552/mfr55210.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>因為人類的過度捕殺和棲息地破壞，夏威夷僧海豹的數量現僅有1,100左右。<ref name=Boland>{{cite journal |last=Boland |first=R |author2=Donohue, R |title=Marine Debris Accumulation in the Nearshore Marine Habitat of the Endangered Hawaiian Monk Seal, Monachus Schauinslandi |journal=Marine Pollution Bulletin |year=2003 |volume=46 |series=11 |pages=1385–139 |doi=10.1016/S0025-326X(03)00291-1 |url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0025326X03002911 |accessdate=2011-05-23 |issue=11 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924154726/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0025326X03002911 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=SchultzExtremely>{{cite journal |last=Schultz J |author2=Baker J |author3=Toonen R |author4=Bowen B |title=Extremely Low Genetic Diversity in the Endangered Hawaiian Monk Seal (Monachus Schauinslandi) |journal=Journal of Heredity |year=2009 |volume=100 |series=1 |pages=25–33 |doi=10.1093/jhered/esn077 |url=http://jhered.oxfordjournals.org/content/100/1/25.full |accessdate=2011-05-23 |issue=1 |first1=J. K. |pmid=18815116 |archive-date=2015-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221042301/http://jhered.oxfordjournals.org/content/100/1/25.full |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=SchultzRange>{{cite journal|last=Schultz|first=J|author2=Baker J |author3=Toonen R |author4=Bowen B  |title=Range-Wide Genetic Connectivity of the Hawaiian Monk Seal and Implications for Translocation|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_conservation-biology_2011-02_25_1/page/124|journal=Conservation Biology|year=2011|volume=25|series=1|pages=124–132 |pmid=21166713 |doi=10.1111/j.1523-1739.2010.01615.x|issue=1 }}</ref>

== 語源學==
夏威夷僧海豹在當地語言中稱為'''{{okina}}Ilio-holo-i-ka-uaua'''，意思是“在波浪中奔跑的狗”。其學名中的種加詞則是來自1899年于在[[萊桑島|萊桑島]]發現了夏威夷僧海豹頭骨的德國科學家雨果·赫爾曼·绍因斯兰（Hugo Hermann Schauinsland）。<ref name=Reeves>{{cite journal |last=Reeves |first=RR |author2=Stewert, BS |title=National Audubon Society Guide to Marine Mammals of the World |year=2002 |isbn=978-0-375-41141-0}}</ref>

==描述==
夏威夷僧海豹有著灰色的毛皮、白色的腹部，身體修長；頭部扁平而較小。<ref name="NOAA Fish">{{cite web |title=Hawaiian Monk Seal (Monachus schauinslandi) |url=http://www.nmfs.noaa.gov/pr/species/mammals/pinnipeds/hawaiianmonkseal.htm |publisher=NOAA Fisheries Office of Protected Resources |accessdate=2011-03-11 |archive-date=2013-08-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6JBcyzsNB?url=http://www.nmfs.noaa.gov/pr/species/mammals/pinnipeds/hawaiianmonkseal.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Kenyon>{{cite journal |last=Kenyon |first=KW |author2=Rice, DW |title=Life History Of the Hawaiian Monk Seal |journal=Pacific Science |volume=13 |url=http://scholarspace.manoa.hawaii.edu/handle/10125/7958 |accessdate=2011-05-23 |date=July 1959 |archive-date=2011-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026140222/http://scholarspace.manoa.hawaii.edu/handle/10125/7958 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其體格使得其可以在[[深海珊瑚礁|深海珊瑚礁]]里尋覓魚蝦及章魚、烏賊等食物。<ref name=Goodman>{{cite journal |last=Goodman-Lowe |first=GD |title=Diet of the Hawaiian Monk Seal (Monachus Schauinslandi) from the Northwestern Hawaiian Islands during 1991 to 1994 |journal=Marine Biology |year=1998 |volume=132 |series=3 |pages=535–46 |url=http://www.csulb.edu/~ggoodman/files/DietHMS.pdf |format=pdf |accessdate=2011-05-23 |doi=10.1007/s002270050419 |issue=3 |archive-date=2012-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010231755/http://www.csulb.edu/~ggoodman/files/DietHMS.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>在不捕獵時，它們會躺在[[西北夏威夷群島|西北夏威夷群島]]的沙灘上曬太陽。<ref name=Baker>{{cite journal|last=Baker|first=J|title=Abundance of the Hawaiian Monk Seal in the Main Hawaiian Islands|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_biological-conservation_2004-03_116_1/page/103|journal=Biological Conservation |year=2004 |volume=116|series=1|pages=103–10|doi=10.1016/S0006-3207(03)00181-2|last2=Johanos|first2=Thea C.}}</ref>成年夏威夷海豹重{{convert|170|-|205|kg}}，體長{{convert|2.1|-|2.3|m}}。<ref name="NOAA Fish"/>

